<br>
What really needs to be done for all 'long spawn' content - is to give every guild the ability to spawn their own version once per week.  Yes, in the long run that might mean you have 5-10 front running guilds, but that really doesn't matter since they're no longer competing for content.<br>
<br>
PoP is supposed to have virtual spaces that hopefully address this, but they've only mentioned them slightly offhanded a couple times.  We'll see in a week or so if they implement them correctly or not.  (Of course if you don't fully apply virtual spaces to all content, you only make the competition for those non-virtual'd things even worse) <p>---<BR>
